Class DivConfig.Builder

  • java.lang.Object
    • eu.kidf.diversicon.core.DivConfig.Builder
  • Enclosing class:
    DivConfig

    public static class DivConfig.Builder
extends Object
    Builder for the config. The builder is not threadsafe and you can use one builder instance to build only one config instance.
